訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"73c47934665684e910a2d1f6148702c6af8941f7","tid":2122031,"uid":142751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ee6d0f4c0277792e3a2496934b7454630c57ca","tid":2122031,"uid":142751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fda5e442976460a5a2584508a87d1aa92f4f486","tid":2122031,"uid":328232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5c1659ade807d269def6ef99911178df72c6da","tid":2122031,"uid":142751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"真係好折磨, 坐唔耐又做唔到嘢 好想死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日開開吓會會頂唔順要拉筋拉下條頸，搞到d同事覺得我怪，之前又拉到條腰，成日好似有野刺住咁痛，貼過殺龍巴斯又做做過針灸都無咩大改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:35:18.000Z","msg":"我個方向係脊椎側彎, 搞左好多年之後先知.<br />\n係個物理治療師同我講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"Hi, 拉左一個月筋確實有改善, 已經基本上冇腰痛"},{"pid":"79077cd9dc56afef16275586191a0bcbb058cace","tid":2122031,"uid":142751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"想離開"},{"pid":"89ed90c1fe96f33959324e10cf68f410728a8c44","tid":2122031,"uid":142751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"離開"}]}